channel.title: [HELP] What kind of server should I develop?
channel.description:
Well since I have a lot of free time on my hands I want to get into server developing again. I will only make 317-359s.
1. PK Server without spawning 2. PK Server with spawning 3. Skill/PK Server 4. Old school PK Server without spawning 5. Old school PK Server with spawning 6. RuneScape 2005-2007 remake
[u]If this is against the rules, delete immediatly.[/u]

item.title: [HELP] What kind of server should I develop?
item.dc:creator: @ghostly150 ghostly150
item.description:
@ghostly150 wrote:

Racist Turtle:

None, make it something that stands out from the rest. Everyone is doing those. I wouldn’t give you an idea because then it wouldn’t be your idea. Also, with whatever you choose, stick to it, apparently you gave up on your last server.

Do what Turtle said. It is better if you come up with your own idea anyway. It is better to be different and you will probably get more players if its something exciting. If it were me, I would try something that was new and interesting than something everyone else is making that is all the same.

Read full topic
